    • Example XML

      <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>

<FacilityIdentifier objID="facility_1" xmlns="http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/organization/v3">
    <FacilityRef>facility_1</FacilityRef>
    <FacilityKeyIdentifier>
        <Identifier organization="Acme" system="sysABC3344" url="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">guid12345</Identifier>
    </FacilityKeyIdentifier>
</FacilityIdentifier>
